name: Admin Console Release 25.1.0
description: This release of the Admin Console brings you a new feature and improvements, see below for details on some of the more notable changes applied to the Admin Console.

ADDED.text: The token expiration time field in the JWT/OIDC app configuration.
Added search feature in the Team Management section of the Admin Console.

IMPROVED.text: For better performance, removed the long date duration options ( All Time and 365 days) from the time dropdown in the insight charts.
Added Historical view of Privacy Policy under customer profile in the Admin Console.
